          },
          "reviewBody": "I am genuinely delighted with my decision to choose The FKS. Reasons\n1. Thoughtful Approach - which FKS leadership and all the teachers carries there - focus on child overall development and beyond academics\n2. Teachers dedication - The dedication of FKS teachers is unparalleled. Their efforts go beyond the classroom—like sunrays reaching every corner of a garden. Have you ever witnessed any event or an annual function spanning four days, meticulously organized to ensure every child’s participation? FKS achieves precisely that.\n3. Practical learning - Personally, I’ve observed FKS encouraging students to observe, think critically, and learn actively. Very nice.\n4. Above all - lot of learnings for parents, Accept it ;)",
